---
title: Quick Sri Lankan Coconut Beef Meatballs with Udon Noodles, Greens & Peanuts
description: Put a subcontinental spin on beef meatballs with a Sri Lankan spice blend and rich tomato paste. Then, factor in some udon
noodles and tasty greens and you've got yourself a new speedy noodle dish that's sure to become a family fave.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/sri-lankan-coconut-beef-meatballs-noodles-50c5d375.jpg
